\};\
\
exports.firstName = \cf10 "Elie"\cf5 ;\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl500\sa400

\f0\fs28 \cf5 \cb1 We can see above that instead of wrapping everything inside of the\'a0
\f3\fs26 \cf7 \cb8 module.exports
\f0\fs28 \cf5 \cb1 \'a0object, we can attach values to the\'a0
\f3\fs26 \cf7 \cb8 exports
\f0\fs28 \cf5 \cb1 \'a0object, which is basically shorthand for\'a0
